Name:
* Chen Xinyi CHN disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to press release published by the Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS) on August 18, 2016. Banned for 2 years from August 11, 2016.
 




Women's 100 m butterfly - Swimming - Rio 2016 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Swimmers competed in preliminary heats, semifinals and final. In the preliminary heats the swimmers with the best official starting times were placed in the last three heats. Normally eight swimmers competed in each heat. The 16 swimmers with the best time in the preliminary heats advanced to the semifinals. From the semifinals the eight swimmers with the best time in the semifinals advanced to the final.  Event facts: Women's 100 m butterfly competition was held at the Olympic Aquatic Stadium.





These results for Women's 100 m butterfly - Rio 2016 Summer Olympics - are based on the official olympic reports and the Olympian Database
